  "heading_path": "机械振动 / 相互垂直的合成 / 同频率相互垂直简谐运动的合成",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 16,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01645:696013ccfb88]]\n\n设两个方向的振动方程分别为：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01646:f92fbe54f0db]]\n令核心中间变量 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01647:e26e47143690]]，相位差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01648:5eb21a4086f3]]:\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01649:50601345d0cb]]\n已知 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01650:3e11bb258c74]]。将其直接代入，并平方消去正弦：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01651:adb5b5b84ad3]]\n将左侧的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01652:54153f847b42]] 替换为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01653:f9aa1f6827d9]]：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01654:06af198a1e2a]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P01655:d6f362ed2036]]^2[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01656:2b4af44cb173]] = [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01657:442601e9beef]]{x^2}{A_1^2}[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01658:e50b5da47b14]]\n该方程的几何图形取决于两分振动的初始相位差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01659:5eb21a4086f3]]。以下为三种典型边界情况的代数讨论：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01660:ff2eb9e78880]]{enumerate}\n    [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01661:ab452bea72eb]] 相位差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01662:2113c0a73bdc]] 或 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01663:ddfff49e49f4]]：将 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01664:76f05a376f88]] 代入：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01665:c13ad62653d8]]S = [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01666:5063f8823b16]]{x^2 + y^2} = [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01667:5063f8823b16]]{A_1^2 + A_2^2} [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01668:d6f362ed2036]]([[PROTECTED:F00001-P01669:11baa595827a]] t + [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01670:10ce0200b450]]_1)$，合运动仍为同频率简谐运动。\n    [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01671:ab452bea72eb]] 相位差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01672:4ec09639227a]] 或 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01673:a89c774e80e7]]：将 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01674:653a5844171c]] 代入方程：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01675:94a1e2488cf8]]\n    [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01676:ab452bea72eb]] 相位差 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01677:c10bd077f3f5]]：将 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01678:a6ad718f90fd]] 代入方程（5），交叉项消除，退化为标准椭圆方程：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01679:263ec955077f]]A_1 = A_2 = A[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01680:2f9718d35e89]]x^2 + y^2 = A^2$。质点在椭圆面上的旋转方向（顺时针或逆时针）由相位差的正负号唯一决定。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01681:06b3847e1b6f]]{enumerate}\n",
